{"tid":1025314,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"模仿上癮 戴巴拿ig新相模擬與C朗慶祝入球","createTime":"2019-02-17T09:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T10:26:35.000Z","uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a0e35223e4b4d40d044b14598dc6c0b0d8e2553","tid":1025314,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190217/large/1550367091_fe9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190217%2Flarge%2F1550367091_fe9b.jpg&h=5f27a421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保羅戴巴拿與C朗<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯前鋒保羅戴巴拿，今季雖然因基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）加盟後，新踢法未適應下表現較失色，不過似乎毫不影響他和C朗的感情，以及他的心情，事關戴巴拿上周六意甲與C朗各入一球後，分別模仿對方的招牌慶祝動作，然後戴巴拿似乎模仿成癮，周日在ig貼出新相，自己躺在地上學習其小狗的睡姿。<br />\n<br />\n祖記上仗主場3:0大勝費辛隆尼，戴巴拿也結束個人的10場入球荒，C朗和戴巴拿的交換慶祝動作相當有趣，戴巴拿學C朗翹起雙手然後跳起180度轉身，再霸氣地分開雙腿着地，而C朗就學戴巴拿用手舉一剔手勢放上唇上。<br />\n<br />\n周日戴巴拿繼續模仿，在家中與自己的小狗同仰臥在地板，以大字型姿勢睡覺，而且戴巴拿以「模仿時間」來形容，相當享受。"},{"pid":"a952c6d11dedfb213275e73980c36420aaa3a1f3","tid":1025314,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T09:10:23.000Z","msg":"終於入到今季第三球<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78fd5e4bd575ddcb1ca292345199e77e48fd70d","tid":1025314,"uid":12000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T09:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jzuo5Mk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzuo5Mk.gif&h=7c0a8783&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7944a98782c032868809e195d98634652ac4c4c","tid":1025314,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T09:53:33.000Z","msg":"「戴巴拿ig新相模擬與C朗慶祝入球」<br />\n<br />\n然後張相係戴巴拿同一隻狗<br />\n<br />\n即係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db48a22f0f530fb55f641819d55bee9a49406b1","tid":1025314,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7944a98782c032868809e19